  m_Name: Cripple
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: 
  archive_name: Cripple
  archive_image: {fileID: 21300000, guid: bea1eafd94993f9418083b5e4ddd84c0, type: 3}
  description: A medium sized fleshy mob born from the fungi, takes the form of an
    incomplete toddler often lacking an arm or leg, and creates a dragging sound
    when travelling. The creature is blind but able to mimic sounds to near perfection
    in order to lure their victims. Uses its malformed, but powerful jaw as a weapon
    and to consume victims.
  risk: 'Risk Level: Mid'
  risk_bullets: '\u2022 Able to mimic Sounds

    \u2022 Unable to Run but learned
    to hide

    \u2022 Heightened hearing, Blind

    \u2022 Prefers to lure prey
    using objects or organisms important to them

'
  solution: Lock all available entrances near the ground. Keep Quiet and Do not engage
    with the creature instead wait for the sounds to stop. If there are sounds do
    not stop.
  unlockDay: 0
